title: Sean O'Neill Band - 100 Irish Drinking Songs - Medley Format
description: Released on garbage labels with no real liner notes or available info on the net, these albums are still a kickass fun little collection of fun drinking songs. Credit should be given the arrangements by Sean O?Neill, who has cleverly put them together in a very complimentary medley format. Each songs flows very naturally into the next. I would imagine children will especially like the collection, and so will you the next time you toss back a few. An excellent training album for the average American on St. Pats. Think of it as music to get shitfaced by.
